TITLE: Defining Types for Todo Records and Actions in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the shape of todo records stored in the Durable Object database and the actions that can be performed on them. It includes types for the record structure and various action payloads.
SOURCE: https://github.com/threepointone/partyserver/blob/main/packages/partysync/README.md#2025-04-15_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
